.TH MORAINE-GUI 1 "2026-06-29" "moraine 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
moraine-gui \- GTK desktop application for Moraine snapshot backups
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B moraine-gui
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B moraine-gui
is the GTK 4 desktop client for Moraine. It edits backup targets, runs backups
with a live log, manages schedules, browses snapshots and restores files. It
shares the configuration file and backup engine with the
.BR moraine (1)
command-line client.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR moraine (1),
.BR rsync (1),
.BR rclone (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Jonaz Thern <info@thern.io>
